                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Police-sergeant, N</hi> 32). I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">Read: "Hereford, March,</hi> 1854; <hi rend="italic">
John Smith convicted of breaking and entering a church, and stealing table-covers and other articles. Five Years' Penal Servitude"</hi>)—the prisoner is the man, I had him in custody—his time would be up in March last.</p>
